data.description:
Welcome to 1781 Uinta St. in the heart of Denver, Colorado. This beautifully updated property offers 4 bedrooms and 2 baths, providing ample space for comfortable living. Recently painted and with replaced air conditioner, furnace, and upstairs windows, the home has a fresh look. With a stunning exterior, a large garage with a capacity of 2 cars, and a thoughtful layout, this home combines functionality and comfort.
Conveniently located in Denver County, it offers easy access to all the amenities and attractions this vibrant city has to offer, including the Denver Zoo. From shopping and dining to outdoor recreational activities, you'll never be far from entertainment and convenience.
Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this incredible property your own. Contact us today to schedule a tour of 1781 Uinta St.
